//
// npu1 variant of objectfifo_cyclostatic_acquire_in_loop. Same #2463
// regression but targeted at Phoenix (npu1) so the fix is exercised on
// both architectures in CI. Reuses the sibling directory's IRON test.py;
// %run_on_npu1% drives @iron.jit to the npu1 device.
//
// REQUIRES: ryzen_ai_npu1, peano, xrt_python_bindings
//
// RUN: %run_on_npu1% %python %S/../objectfifo_cyclostatic_acquire_in_loop/test.py
